ul.li:
E18. A method for a network entity of a radio communication network comprising the steps of:
receiving a handover request message identifying a first resource and a second resource, the first resource distinct and different from the second resource;
selecting one of the first and second resources;
allocating a radio channel associated with the handover;
selecting a bearer for a terrestrial interface; and
seizing resources for the interface.

E23. A method for a network entity of a radio communication network comprising the steps of:
receiving an assignment request message identifying a first resource and a second resource, the first resource distinct and different from the second resource;
selecting one of the first and second resources;
allocating a radio channel associated with the assignment;
selecting a bearer for a terrestrial interface; and
seizing resources for the interface.

